<div class="container">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
      <div class="img-fluid" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556484687-30636164638b?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=967&q=80'); height: 500px; background-size: cover;"></div>
        <div >
          <h3 class="title"><strong>What's Kaabo?</strong></h3>
            <p>Kaabo means “Welcome” in Youruba.  Kaabo app, it is a place to improve imigrants access to information in Portugal...</p>
          <h3 class="title"><strong>How does it work?</strong></h3>
                <p>Kaabo provides you clear and concrete official and community information regarding basic rights.  Enter a secton below and start your journey.</p>
          <div id="forum-card">
            <h3><strong>Kaabo Forum</strong></h3>
                <p>Visit the Forum or join the Community. Search and share information, find support and make friends!</p>
          </div>
          <h3 class="title"><strong>Useful Information</strong></h3>
          <div class="cards">
          <% @topics.each do |topic| %>
          <div class="card">
            <h2><%= topic.category %></h2>
            <% topicname = topic.category %>
            <%= image_tag "icons/icon#{topicname}.svg"%>
            <div class="links">
              <p><%= link_to "#{topic.category}", topic_themes_path(topic) %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
